    {
        "createdBy": 14,
        "createdDate": "2024-12-24T04:38:05.000+0000",
        "documentKey": "TSYNC-SR-9",
        "fields": {
            "SubsysReqStat$86": "0%",
            "description": "<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://acceleratedsoftware.jamacloud.com/attachment/141/Jama-clEAR-Installation.png\" width=\"250\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Hearing aids can be durable&nbsp;and stocky, or they can be small, thin, and invisible. In order to gain market share with those 35 and under, we need a hearing aid to reflect the active lifestyle.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Durability covers a wide arena of activities. Some examples:</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>During contact sports now, the device must be removed, with the abutment covered.</li>\n\t<li>At the hairdresser, extra caution must be exercised.</li>\n\t<li>Various weather conditions can negatively affect it (wind [dust], humidity, etc.).</li>\n\t<li>追加のコメント</li>\n</ul>\n",
            "documentKey": "TSYNC-SR-9",
            "globalId": "GID-61347",
            "name": "Durable",
            "status": 293
        },
        "globalId": "GID-61347",
